show.description: A desperate young woman agrees to spend a night blindfolded with a stranger to save her mother's life—only to unknowingly fall for the wrong man, a powerful fashion tycoon. Years later, fate reunites them as secrets, ambition, and hidden parentage threaten to destroy everything.
